# Keep the docker build context small. The node image (docker/node/Dockerfile) only needs
# artifacts/deb/<rid>/opt/packetnet/app + docker/node/packetnet.container.yaml, so exclude
# the heavy build cruft (NOT artifacts/deb, which the COPY needs).
.git
**/obj
**/bin
**/node_modules
**/.vs
artifacts/node
artifacts/*.deb
artifacts/*.tar.gz
artifacts/*.tar.zst
artifacts/deb/*/DEBIAN
tools
